# Web product injection point.
#
# IosPackager empties this folder and copies the WebPackager output here
# (index.html, assets/*.js, *.wasm, shaders/, game-assets/, pack-index.json).
# It is referenced as a *folder reference* in project.pbxproj, so the whole
# tree is copied verbatim into the app bundle at ForgeaxPlayer.app/public/ and
# served over forgeax-app://public/ by ForgeaxSchemeHandler.
